28 5–817.
29 (a) In accordance with this section, a school board:

HOUSE BILL 1074 7
1 (1) may adopt conflict of interest regulations applicable to officials and
2 employees of the school system; and
3 (2) shall adopt conflict of interest regulations applicable to members of the
4 school board.
5 (b) (1) The conflict of interest regulations adopted by a school board under
6 subsection [(a)(1)] (A) of this section:
7 (i) shall be [similar to the provisions of] EQUIVALENT TO OR
8 EXCEED THE REQUIREMENTS OF Subtitle 5 of this title; but
9 (ii) in accordance with regulations adopted by the Ethics
10 Commission and consistent with the intent of this title, may be modified to the extent
11 necessary to make the regulations relevant to the prevention of conflicts of interest in that
