13 (2) [The] IN ADDITION TO THE REQUIREMENTS UNDER PARAGRAPH
14 (1) OF THIS SUBSECTION, THE conflict of interest regulations adopted by a school board
15 under subsection (a)(2) of this section SHALL:
16 (i) [shall be equivalent to or exceed the requirements of Subtitle 5
17 of this title; but
18 (ii) in accordance with regulations adopted by the Ethics
19 Commission and consistent with the intent of this title, may be modified to the extent
20 necessary to make the regulations relevant to the prevention of conflicts of interest in that
